OL,4,CPIP: Rules to be eased for terminally
OL,5,Cill benefit claimants
OL,6, Terminally ill people with less than a
OL,7, year to live will get fast-tracked for
OL,8, benefits after ministers said they will
OL,9, expand the timeframe for those eligible
OL,10, for special consideration.
OL,12,FPreviously patients had to prove they
OL,13,Fhad less than six months to live and
OL,14,Fcharities say many died without their
OL,15,Fcases being resolved.
OL,17,FIt is two years since a government
OL,18,Freview was launched into the issue.
OL,20,FCampaigners say it is a "significant
OL,21,Fstep forward".
